version_description: Wonderful song from the movie Eat, Pray, Love enjoy strumming eddie's words.
I'd play the Dsus2 without the open high E and the E major chord without the B...it just seems to sound better.
Uses correct chords to the original version, which didn't have a Bm in it at all.
There was no tab on this version of the song so I figured I'd figure it out and share it. This is my first one and I don't think it ended up too bad.
